--[[
    MenuClient (LocalScript)
    
    Press M → opens menu.
    Skill Tree shows ALL 3 trees side by side as columns.
    Moves listed under each column.
    Click a move to equip it to your hotbar.
    
    Hotbar: 12 slots (1-9, 0, -, =) at the bottom of the screen.
    Only for moves. No items.
]]

